Package Files

Class MyFile

java.lang.Object
Files.Editable
Files.File
All Implemented Interfaces:
Editable, Viewable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Docum, Image, Media, SimpleFile
public class MyFile
extends EditableFile
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
Base file Class, it is used to store basic file data: file size, file name, file directory, creation time, modification time, execution program
